ZH: 我谢罪刚才的无礼行为。
EN: I apologize for my rude behavior just now.

ZH: 请允许我向您表示最诚挚的谢罪。
EN: Please allow me to express my most sincere apology to you.

ZH: 对不起，我真的很抱歉。
EN: I'm very sorry, I apologize sincerely.

ZH: 对不起，我错了。我向你谢罪。
EN: I'm sorry, I was wrong. I apologize to you.

ZH: 请原谅我刚才那样的无礼。
EN: Please forgive me for my rudeness just now.

ZH: 我对我的过失深感抱歉。
EN: I deeply apologize for my mistake.

ZH: 请接受我的谢罪，我会尽量弥补我的过错。
EN: Please accept my apology, I will try to make up for my mistake.

ZH: 对不起，我没有考虑周到，对此深感抱歉。
EN: I'm sorry, I didn't think carefully, I apologize for that.

ZH: 我谢罪刚才对您造成的困扰。
EN: I apologize for the trouble I caused you just now.

ZH: 对不起，我有责任，我向你谢罪。
EN: I'm sorry, I take responsibility, I apologize to you.

