EN: Please accept my most sincere apology.

ZH: 我对我的行为深感自责，我向您谢罪。
EN: I am deeply regretful of my actions, I apologize to you.

ZH: 我对您说的话表示怀疑，我向您深感抱歉。
EN: I apologize sincerely for doubting what you said.

